      <h1>GitHub Copilot vs Cursor 2026: Which AI Coding Assistant Is Better?</h1>
      <p class="meta">Updated July 2026</p>
    </header>

    <p class="lead">
      If you are choosing between GitHub Copilot and Cursor in 2026, you are comparing two leading solutions that serve millions of users worldwide. Both products have matured significantly and offer unique strengths for different use cases. Based on product documentation, specification analysis, feature evaluation, and workflow assessment, here is the detailed comparison you need to make an informed decision.
    </p>

