        <tr><td>Multi-file Editing</td><td>Limited to single-file context</td><td>Multi-file refactoring and edits</td></tr>
        <tr><td>AI Agent Features</td><td>Basic chat in sidebar</td><td>Built-in AI chat with project context and agent workflows</td></tr>
