    <p>On value, GitHub Copilot delivers more features per dollar for typical inline completion workflows. Cursor's premium is justified when your work depends on multi-file context, agent-driven refactoring, and natural language project-wide edits — capabilities Copilot does not offer. For a broader view of pricing across the category, our <a href="/reviews/best-ai-coding-assistant-2026">best AI coding assistants</a> guide compares plans from every major contender.</p>
